OL,7,FThe Health Secretary has confirmed he
OL,8,Fwill ask the High Court to declare a
OL,9,Flooming nurses' strike unlawful, in a
OL,10,Fdramatic escalation of tensions with
OL,11,Fthe Royal College of Nursing.
OL,13,FThe Government and NHS Employers
OL,14,Fclaim that the 48-hour walkout, due
OL,15,Fto begin at 8pm on Sunday (30 April)
OL,16,Fand end next Tuesday evening (2 May),
OL,17,Fbreaches the legal mandate that the
OL,18,Funion received from members to take
OL,19,Fstrike action.
OL,3,CHealth Secretary will ask High Court
OL,4,Cto declare nurses' strike illegal as
OL,5,Ctensions escalate
